title: Christmas Wish #11 - The Nicolson Family
description: Jess nominated her friend Genna who's Dad started having health issues a year ago.  Her dad moved in with her and now she is his full-time caretaker while also working full-time.  Then a few weeks ago, her husband wasn't feeling good, went into the doctor and found out he has Stage 4 Cancer.
